<A>__{two policemen move quickly and professionally up the corridor toward thorwald's apartment. they stop at the door, listen a moment, and then push the buzzer insistently. inside the apartment, lights go on, and thorwald is in the center of the room looking toward the door. lisa staggers away from him, trying to rearrange her clothes and her hair. she is as surprised at the interruption as thorwald. he listens, looks back questioningly toward lisa, then goes to the door. he passes into the kitchen.}
